  "markdown": "Our Quantum Advantage challenge with $20,000 BTC award is live.\n[More Details \u2192](https://app.bluequbit.io/hackathons/GFgHTGbTylwmMsCp)\n[![Logo Deqart](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/639a397b9711984d91a35d74/63a042ea84d8d44f97a1cc3e_Group%2097846.svg)](https://www.bluequbit.io/)\n[Home](https://www.bluequbit.io/)[Hackathons](https://www.bluequbit.io/quantum-advantage-challenge)[Pricing](https://www.bluequbit.io/pricing)[Platform](https://www.bluequbit.io/platform)[Blog](https://www.bluequbit.io/blog)[Research](https://www.bluequbit.io/research)[Contact Us](https://www.bluequbit.io/contact-us)[Platform Access](https://app.bluequbit.io/)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/639a397b9711984d91a35d74/639adfd6b9bb747186953ef8_Icons.svg)![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/639a397b9711984d91a35d74/63e8e60dbe8e5c311ed976e2_icon_Close.svg)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63d774102fb109fd799a5006/6968f4f3f3a76069dd656529_Arul%20Rhik%20Mazumder.png)\n# Arul Rhik Mazumder\nTechnical Writer\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/639a397b9711984d91a35d74/63d75e6d32dbbf66f62de758_Social_In.svg)](https://www.linkedin.com/in/arul-mazumder-370294239/)\nRhik is a graduating Carnegie Mellon computer science student with research experience at Caltech's Institute of Quantum Information and Matter and Carnegie Mellon Quantum Technologies Group. Beginning his quantum journey in high school, he has authored six peer-reviewed publications while founding CMU Quantum, Carnegie Mellon's first undergraduate quantum computing club with over 200 members and sponsorships from Boeing and General Motors. As Technical Writer at BlueQubit, Rhik bridges cutting-edge quantum research and accessible education, creating content that demystifies quantum computing for the broader community.\n###### Company\n[Docs](https://app.bluequbit.io/docs)[Blog](https://www.bluequbit.io/blog)[SDK Docs](https://app.bluequbit.io/sdk-docs/index.html)[Contact us](https://www.bluequbit.io/contact-us)[Research](https://www.bluequbit.io/research)[Quantum mechanical model](https://www.bluequbit.io/blog/quantum-mechanical-model)[BlueQubit platform](https://www.bluequbit.io/platform)[Quantum computing simulators](https://www.bluequbit.io/blog/quantum-computing-simulators)[Free access to quantum computers](https://www.bluequbit.io/free-access)[Quantum computing software platforms](https://www.bluequbit.io/blog/quantum-computing-software-platforms)[Quantum computing algorithms](https://www.bluequbit.io/quantum-computing-algorithms)[Quantum computing companies](https://www.bluequbit.io/blog/quantum-computing-companies)\n###### Explore\n###### Services\n###### Resources\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/639a397b9711984d91a35d74/6745b8a1e32856e841b07003_product-hunt-logo-orange.svg)](https://www.producthunt.com/products/bluequbit/reviews)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/639a397b9711984d91a35d74/63a042ea84d8d44f97a1cc3e_Group%2097846.svg)\n\u00a92025 by BlueQubit. All rights reserved.\n[ ](https://discord.gg/TkMuBmWhCw?utm_source=Discord%20Widget&utm_medium=Connect)\n",
